data.description: Move-in ready house with a HEATED POOL in a very desirable neighborhood! This one owner home is great condition featuring new architectural shingles in 2015, newer Kenmore appliances in kitchen, brand new carpet in all bedrooms, newer water heater and recently cleaned and serviced HVAC. with a large living area, eat-in kitchen and a spacious formal dining room make this home great to entertain family and friends! Cool off in the in-ground salt water pool in the summer and cozy up to the fireplace in cooler months! Large sunroom with lots of windows. HUGE backyard with a privacy fence. Call today to schedule your private viewing.  Home won't last long in this desirable, extremely safe, neighborhood in close proximity to Tyndall Air Force Base, shopping and dining.
